h1(#wxlogtextctrl). Wx::LogTextCtrl

Using these target all the log messages can be redirected to a text control.
The text control must have been created with @TE_MULTILINE@ style by the
caller previously.

h2. Derived from

"Log":log.html

h2. See also

"LogTextCtrl":logtextctrl.html,

"StreamToTextRedirector":streamtotextredirector.html

