h3(#LogTextCtrl_new). LogTextCtrl.new

  *LogTextCtrl.new*(%(arg-type)"TextCtrl":textctrl.html% textctrl)

Constructs a log target which sends all the log messages to the given text
control. The _textctrl_ parameter cannot be @NULL@.


